la Alberto|Alberto]] 11\n|HT= 13\u201314\n|twomin1= 4\n|yellow1= 4\n|red1= \n|twomin2= 2\n|yellow2= 4\n|red2= \n|stadium= [[Palacio Multiusos de Guadalajara|Palacio Multiusos]], [[Guadalajara, Castile-La Mancha|Guadalajara]]\n|attendance= 2,400\n|referee= Geipel, Helbig\n|refnat= GER\n}}\n----\n{{handballbox\n|date= 27 May 2012\n|time= 10:15\n|team1= {{hbw-rt|ARG}}\n|score= 21 \u2013 30\n|team2= {{hbw|NED}}\n|report= [http://www.ihf.info/files/CompetitionData/133/pdf/05OMR.PDF Report]\n|goals1= [[Magdalena Decilio|Decilio]] 5\n|goals2= [[Yvette Broch|Broch]] 6\n|HT= 9\u201315\n|twomin1= 4\n|yellow1= 3\n|red1= \n|twomin2= 4\n|yellow2= 3\n|red2= \n|stadium= [[Palacio Multiusos de Guadalajara|Palacio Multiusos]], [[Guadalajara, Castile-La Mancha|Guadalajara]]\n|attendance=475 \n|referee= Bonaventura C, Bonaventura J\n|refnat= FRA\n}}\n----\n{{handballbox\n|date= 27 May 2012\n|time= 12:30\n|team1= {{hbw-rt|ESP}}\n|score= 22 \u2013 23\n|team2= {{hbw|CRO}}\n|report=[http://www.ihf.info/files/CompetitionData/133/pdf/06OMR.PDF Report]\n|goals1= [[Carmen Mart\u00edn|Mart\u00edn]] 9\n|goals2= [[Maja Zebi\u0107|Zebi\u0107]] 8\n|HT= 10\u201312\n|twomin1= 3\n|yellow1= 2\n|red1= \n|twomin2= 8\n|yellow2= 2\n|red2= \n|stadium= [[Palacio Multiusos de Guadalajara|Palacio Multiusos]], [[Guadalajara, Castile-La Mancha|Guadalajara]]\n|attendance= 3,000\n|referee= Geipel, Helbig\n|refnat= GER\n}}\n\n=== 2012 IHF Qualification Tournament #3 ===\n\n*Venue: {{flagicon|DEN}} [[Gigantium]], [[Aalborg]], [[Denmark]]\n*All times are [[Central European Time]] ([[UTC+01:00]]).\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n!width=\"220\"|Team\n!width=\"30\"|Pld\n!width=\"30\"|W\n!width=\"30\"|D\n!width=\"30\"|L\n!width=\"30\"|GF\n!width=\"30\"|GA\n!width=\"30\"|GD\n!width=\"30\"|Pts\n|- style=\"background-color:#CCCCFF;\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{hbw|RUS}}\n|3||3||0||0||101||57||+44||'''6'''\n|- style=\"background-color:#CCCCFF;\" \n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{hbw|DEN}}\n|3||2||